{"tid":2193271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"學汪威遜話 揸得快唔代表唔安全 咁個巴士司機有幾危險","createTime":"2020-09-07T16:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T16:46:35.000Z","uid":27223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f99265df5f35ab9ffd8b0f72a99b4dfa6cd6c3c9","tid":2193271,"uid":27223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T16:34:51.000Z","msg":"咁巴士司機都係30姐 有幾危險呀<br />\n<br />\n回帶： <br />\n速龍小隊今日凌晨在油麻地驅散示威者，片段拍攝到有接載警員的白色小巴全速衝向人群，據報釀成人踩人，導致多人受傷。<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">行動部高級警司汪威遜今日於記者會上稱「揸得快唔代表唔安全（drive fast doesn't mean it's unsafe）」</span></strong></span>，強調所有警員都經過專業訓練，市民應對警方有信心、支持警方執法。汪威遜又否認做法是罔顧人命，「警方由頭到尾，都無做過一件事係罔顧人命」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/速龍小巴衝向人群-汪威遜-揸得快唔代表唔安全-江永祥-無觀察到人踩人/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%80%9F%E9%BE%8D%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%B4%E8%A1%9D%E5%90%91%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4-%E6%B1%AA%E5%A8%81%E9%81%9C-%E6%8F%B8%E5%BE%97%E5%BF%AB%E5%94%94%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E5%94%94%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8-%E6%B1%9F%E6%B0%B8%E7%A5%A5-%E7%84%A1%E8%A7%80%E5%AF%9F%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%BA%E8%B8%A9%E4%BA%BA%2F&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqLvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=753de1bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%80%9F%E9%BE%8D%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%B4%E8%A1%9D%E5%90%91%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4-%E6%B1%AA%E5%A8%81%E9%81%9C-%E6%8F%B8%E5%BE%97%E5%BF%AB%E5%94%94%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E5%94%94%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8-%E6%B1%9F%E6%B0%B8%E7%A5%A5-%E7%84%A1%E8%A7%80%E5%AF%9F%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%BA%E8%B8%A9%E4%BA%BA%2F&h=166d59aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/速龍小巴衝向人群-汪威遜-揸得快唔代表唔安全-江永祥-無觀察到人踩人/</a>"},{"pid":"a63db4e718bd73f2606b3bfa9800c06c166c5c10","tid":2193271,"uid":92936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f99265df5f35ab9ffd8b0f72a99b4dfa6cd6c3c9","tid":2193271,"uid":27223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T16:34:51.000Z",